		<td bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/lotr/gfx/mom/whi_08.gif"><font class="bfont"><font class="h1font"> CHapel , NC 6/28/03<br></font><br><font class="h2font"> <b>Overall Rating:</b> </font><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><font size='1'>(3.20)</font><br><font class="h2font"> <b>Author:</b> <A HREF='http://www.decktech.net/lotr/main/mpage.php?member=14018'>josh "capin" boyd</A></font><font class="afont"> <a href='http://www.decktech.net/lotr/main/mpage.php?member=14018&sub=1'> (Subscribe to this member)</a><br><font class="h2font"> <b>Date Submitted:</b> July 2, 2003</font><p align='justify'><blockquote><font class="bfont"> Ok so my dad has agreed to let us to go to one tourney a month....i guess thats better than none. but anyway he wouldnt let us do gencon/decipher con or anything big cause he doesnt understand TCG. Anyway we got up last saturday and im like hey jon! (my brother) its the last saturday of the month. and jons like oh no! I dont have a good deck! darn! and I say &quot;thats..cool.&quot; anyway he just decides to bring a deck but with extra sleeves and commons uncommons<br />
<br />
its prolly 10:30 and the tourney starts at 1:00 so we ride our bikes down to winn dixie and get some free sodas from the vending machine (it only does it with code red MT. dew though) anyway we drink our sodas, get hyped enough to ride around alot more until like 11:30 and then we head home, get in the car , go get gas for the van, and get more sodas =) <br />
when we get to borders its 12:25 so we have some time to kill. When we walk to the back theres no tables there nor any other people. So I was like darn a 2 person tourney. But then I see an afro bobbing through the stacks of  books. and then emerges a rather pasty faced white kid with an afro.. and im like &quot;he looks like  a lotr player..hmm&quot; <br />
Anyway I see hes carrying his deck so im sure he is (it was edwin) he asks to see my binder and I show him. and he goes &quot;woah you gat alot of brands!&quot; (there were 3 flaming brands in my binder) and i was like &quot;who the heck kind of idiot plays nazzys in standard??? and he grins real weird. then I look at his deck an its nazzy so...<br />
<br />
Anyway at about 1:30 we start with like 16 people.<br />
<br />
game 1<br />
me VS Jeff reynolds<br />
Im playing HIDAN/ uruk bomb<br />
hes  playing some kinda rohan/elf but the elfs are like lorien guardiens?<br />
(im starting frodo,ring,eomer,eowyn and so is he)<br />
we bid he goes first gets out his site (pull legolas ARGH!!) <br />
pulls lego, plays a lorien guardien or somthin. moves.<br />
I play 2 uruks he shoots one down with lego. he assigns the one to eomer.<br />
eomer takes one and eowyn prevents other.<br />
he looks bad and stops.<br />
Anyway thats about how it goes.<br />
But i make it to 9 first and he has no minions.<br />
<br />
FW +3<br />
props -<br />
my good gaming<br />
