<br />
game 2 -<br />
me VS curtis jones<br />
hes playing healing rohan/gandalf<br />
 (he starts eomer and eowyn DOE)<br />
we bid. I go first, pull gorn. I got a prety good hand<br />
move and he plays some people but theres to much pool left and Im afraid of cave troll.<br />
so I stop<br />
he plays stuff then moves and moves.<br />
it goes on till site 5  which he gets to first.<br />
i bomb 6 yes 6 feirce uruk hai on him =)<br />
he makes it out but hes wounded badly<br />
anyway he gets to 8 and has the option to move <br />
he stops (well hes got like 8 guys stacked on the swarms!)<br />
he wins big time.. 10 minions to 5 comps<br />
FL +1<br />
<br />
props -<br />
curtisses cool incident with grima doing eowyn and him just playing them back to heal her twice :)<br />
<br />
