<br />
<br />
game 3 -<br />
me VS edwin <br />
hes playin rohan gondor/ nazzys -<br />
I think i went first. played some stuff and stopped at 2 cause I had no brands<br />
 The highlight of the game is when I drew my brands and put one on aragorn with his sword (i didnt put one on eomer cause he plays 2 grims WT)  but anyway I beat everyone but WK after that and I managed well. I could have killed him when he was at 8 first. but like he said its more manly to run for it. lol . So I run  from 7 to 9 and win easily (i think he only killed sam?)<br />
FW +3<br />
